tbamud-rwb build notes: MSVC 8 (Visual Studio 2005) (obsolete)
================================================================

This file existed in stock TbaMUD to describe compiling the C server with MSVC 8 (Visual Studio 2005).
The Rust rewrite builds only with Cargo and targets modern Rust toolchains, so
MSVC 8 (Visual Studio 2005) is not supported.  Build on a current operating system with:

    cargo build --release

See ../README.md and doc/porting.txt.
